<title>INDIA: India's ICICI 96/97 net up 62 pct.</title>
<headline>India's ICICI 96/97 net up 62 pct.</headline>
<dateline>BOMBAY 1997-05-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Industrial Credit and Investment Corporation of India (ICICI) said on Monday its 1996/97 (April-March) net profit, after adjustments for the previous year rose to 7.7 billion rupees from 4.74.</p>
<p>Profit after tax, but before adjustments rose to 7.52 billion rupees from 4.36.</p>
<p>Disbursals for the year were 111.81 billion rupees and earnings per share (EPS) 16.30 rupees.  </p>
<p>The 1996/97 results are post-merger figures. SCICI merged with ICICI with effect from April 1, 1996.</p>
